<h1 align=center> Add a new PERSON record</h1>

This page allows you to create a brand new PERSON record in the database.<p>

<Big>PLEASE NOTE:</BIG> The form below asks for only the <u>minimal</u> information required for a new person (e.g. name, full_name, and MEDLINE name). You may specify other information (e.g. phone, fax, etc.) <b>after</b> you create the person record, by viewing the record and using the standard record updating mechanism to edit/specify additional fields.
<p>
The following information is <B>REQUIRED</B> to create the new PERSON record. Please enter the requested information in the boxes below, and then  click on the "SUBMIT" button.

<FORM METHOD=POST ACTION="/<!--|WEBDRIVER_PATH_FROM_ROOT|-->" TARGET=content>
<p>
<b>Full Name:</b><br>
This field should hold the full name of the person, with the last name first. For instance, John Pat Dole would be "Dole, John Pat". 
<INPUT type=text name="full_name" size="60">
<p>
<b>MEDLINE name:</b><br>
This field should hold the name of the person in MEDLINE format. For instance, John Pat Dole would be "Dole-J-P.".<br>
<INPUT type=text name="name" size="60">
<p>
<b>Address:</b><br>
This field holds the PERSON's surface mail address. Be sure to include all necessary zip codes or country codes. <br>
<TEXTAREA name=address WRAP=virtual rows=6 cols=70></TEXTAREA>

<p>
<input type=submit value="SUBMIT">
<input type=hidden name=MIval value=aa-process-person.apg>

</FORM>


<?/MIBLOCK>  <!-- ends cond authorize -->

</HTML>
